$interpreted: Sanchez: I'm beat, let me rest a bit.
Rune: ...Hiding here...is safe...
Sanchez: What the hell are you saying?...Wait, are you saying...
Sanchez: Ah, yes! Threatening these rambling performers will be a piece of cake. They'll be easily scared into letting us stay here.
Sanchez: (While they're not paying attention, we'd better...)
Ru-yi: Ahhh!!!!!
Sanchez: Everybody, don't move!
Sanchez: ...Wait a second, I know you. You're that strange looking circus troupe...
Sanchez: Trash, there's no way they'll——
Hanbei: Attack!
Sanchez: Wahhh!!!!
Hanbei: Who are you!?
Hutchinson: ...Wait, I think I know this guy...
Sanchez: Oh, shut it! Last time we met you were beating me to a pulp!
Sanchez: Bastard, let me go!
Rune: Sanchez...is crushed...
Sanchez: Rune, teach them a lesson!
Rune: ..So..phie...
Sanchez: Rune, you traitor! Oh, I see. Rune has found a woman. Great. Now...
Sanchez: HELP!!!
Sophie: Rune!? What are you doing here?
Sophie: What on earth happened?
Rune: Master...died...we...ran.
Sophie: Oh, no! Well, let's get this settled first.
Hanbei: Sophie, you're not thinking about taking them in, are you?
Sophie: I know, but if you see somebody in need you have to help!
Hanbei: Do you? Sophie, don't you remember? You said you don't want to be nice to everybody.
Sophie: Don't worry, I'm not like my father. Just let them stay the night. They'll leave tomorrow.
Hanbei: ...whatever!
Ru-yi: Hanbei!
Sophie: ......
Hutchinson: It'll be fine. Ru-yi and I will get him.
Elio: (...Those people in purple clothes, perhaps they're part of the sect...)
Sophie: Elio?
Elio: Umm...sorry. I'm just a bit flustered. You don't have to go get your troupe?
Sophie: ......
Sophie: Nah~Hanbei is just getting out his anger. He'll be back in a bit.
Sophie: You look so serious. What's on your mind?
Elio: Nothing...
Elio: Rune has blood on his clothes. I've studied Life Magic. Let me heal him.
Sophie: Got it. Rune, sit right here.
Elio: There's no wound?
Elio: These old scars...no, they're not scars. They're tattoos...
Sophie: Ahh!
Rune: ...Sophie...?
Elio: Sophie, what's wrong?
Sophie: No...nuh..nuh...nuh...nothing, I just suddenly...
Sophie: I...I...I...I...I...I just wasn't ready...
Sophie: I just didn't think this place would be so in...in...interesting~ Just curious that's all!
Rune: ...Sophie...your face...is...red....
Elio: Rune's got a point. That's not the reaction of someone who's just curious...
Sophie: It...it...it...it's just my constitution! That's what happens when I get curious!
Sanchez: I've never heard of that...
Elio: The patterns on these tattoos look like Runes.
Sophie: Huh?
Elio: They are of a different system than commonly seen Runes, but the logic is the same. Rune, how'd you get these tattoos?
Rune: Rune...doesn't know...
Sanchez: Good luck with that. He's in the lowest class of slaves.
Sanchez: He's always had a master. Nobody has ever looked at him like a person, so he doesn't really know how to speak.
Elio: ...I think he is from the north.
Sophie: A northerner?
Elio: I've only seen this once.
Elio: Legend has it that the north has a mysterious method for using Runes...by tattooing them on one's body...
Lazer: Get'em!
Sophie: Ahhhh!!!
Elio: Oof...
Lazer: Not bad. There aren't any cracks. Come in.
Sophie: Everybody...!
Sophie: Let them go! It has nothing to do with them! This is inhumane!?
Lazer: ...I gave up being human a long time ago.
Lazer: Take these criminals away.
Soldier: Yes, sir!
Lazer: Her Majesty does not want to cause a stir, so I'll let you go this time. But if this gets out...
Lazer: My sickle has no problem with fresh blood...
